<A>__{prussians against austrians, or french, or saxons. roderick fighting.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{i do not intend to make a history of battles in the prussian any more than in the english service. i did my duty in them as well as another, and there was not a braver, cleverer, handsomer, and, i must own, wickeder soldier in the prussian army.}
<L>__{exterior battlefield action day}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{i had formed myself to the condition of the proper fighting beast; on a day of action, i was savage and happy.}
<A>__{roderick saves captain galgenstein's life.}
